Text: Welcome to Traffic School To Go PM Jeffrey Dasovich Your registration for the Traffic School To Go program has been recorded We hope that everything is clear and that you will have no problem successfully completing the program but if you need help please reply to this Email with your questions or phone toll free Remember this is EXACTLY how you will need to reenter your information when logging back in to the program license state California license number N To log into the course visit the following URL students If you find you have made an error in entering your license information use the incorrect information to log in Once logged in you will have the option of correcting the error by hitting the Personal Information button on your Student Control Panel at the bottom of any page Thereafter the corrected license information will log you in Oh and just to confirm we have the following mailing address information for you Dolores St San Francisco CA If this is incorrect use your Personal Information button to fix it In fact please be sure to doublecheck and change if necessary all of your Personal Information sometime before you finish so that we can reach you if theres a problem or so that your certificate does not go astray due to a typo in your mailing address Thanks Sincerely Peggy Goldman Traffic School To Go

You have started Dasovich Jeffrey N CAyou have begun the first Round of the finest traffic school in the known universe Please doublecheck personal information and court instructions in this Email to be sure you understand your deadlines and that your information is correct If you see a mistake you can correct it either from the Edit Citation Information button or the Personal Information button on your Student Control Panel at the bottom of every page Name Jeffrey Dasovich Day phone Night phone Court Solano CountyVallejoBenicia Citation Due Nov Make sure you understand where your Certificate of Completion will be mailed no matter which mailing option you select by reviewing your courts specifications below When you have successfully completed the Traffic School To Go program AND we have received your payment we will mail the courts copy of the Certificate of Completion DIRECTLY TO THE COURT on your behalf We will also mail you a copy of the certificate and a receipt for your payment We send Certificates out Monday through Saturday except holidays Be sure to finish in time for your Certificate to get either to you or to your Court in time to meet your due date Thanks again for choosing Traffic School To Go Craig Buck CAN
